# Normalize all text files to LF in the working tree on every platform. Without
# this, Git's autocrlf checks out CRLF on Windows and the byte-for-byte doc
# comparison tests (docs/cli.md, docs/db-schema.md) fail there.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Older git versions try to fix line endings on images and videos, this prevents it.
*.jpg binary
*.mp4 binary
*.zip binary
*.gif binary
